Frullani积分定理:
\series default
 设
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(x)-f(\infty)=\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}\frac{u(k)(-x)^{k}}{k!},\qquad g(x)-g(\infty)=\sum_{k=0}^{\infty}\frac{v(k)(-x)^{k}}{k!},
\]

