 则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\lim_{n\to0+}I_{n}\equiv\lim_{n\to0+}\int_{0}^{\infty}x^{n-1}\{f(ax)-g(bx)\}\ud x=\{f(0)-f(\infty)\}\left\{ \log\frac{b}{a}+\frac{\ud}{\ud s}\left(\log\frac{v(s)}{u(s)}\right)_{s=0}\right\} 
\]

\end_inset


